item.title: JP-series-integrated-distribution-box-compensation-control-terminal-lighting
item.description: JP series outdoor comprehensive distribution box is designed to meet the requirements of standardization, miniaturization and outdoor type of rural low-voltage power distribution equipment. It integrates power distribution, metering, protection, overload, short circuit, phase loss, undervoltage, Current over-current protection, zero line disconnection protection on the power supply side, automatic reclosing and opening, lightning protection, and capacitor reactive power compensation are integrated, providing a guarantee for safe electricity use in rural areas.
